{"tid":1549700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果一星期入面有幾日去黨鐵商場靜坐","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T14:22:51.000Z","uid":47775,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf4f9d177caca195ca404ee58634251070a028d","tid":1549700,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"喊口號，唱歌，人夠多可能令周圍啲鋪頭提早閂門<br />\n仲可能令黨鐵申請禁制令，禁止市民進入<br />\n<br />\n有無得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce31514d02fdec8b4cde75f9613d1b1d04fdd21a","tid":1549700,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e45cf145869da0cf5595bc2fbeffa6b63b41b7dc","tid":1549700,"uid":229436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"咩都唔做去涼冷氣睇商品但不購物就得"},{"pid":"6bd94954d4f692b0fc00cf00bf68d84b70a06bf4","tid":1549700,"uid":157891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e45cf145869da0cf5595bc2fbeffa6b63b41b7dc","tid":1549700,"uid":229436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"咩都唔做去涼冷氣睇商品但不購